metadata.name: Baikal Breeze
metadata.description:
This NFT represents the Original Canvas Painting I did in 04/2016.

70x50 cm (28x20 inch)  
Oil on canvas  
2016

This painting symbolizes the beauty of the natural phenomenon, expressed in the femininity of the image, and the power of the tide driven by the wind, expressed in the height of the ice on the rocks.
